videos.description: Perry Ellis goes in and tries to score for Kansas, but he loses the ball.  Abedel Nadar picks it up and passes to Monte Morris, who finishes with the nice shot to put Iowa State up 62-57.
videos.headline: Iowa State taking advantage of Kansas miscues

videos.description: 2H (8:09) ISU Ball gets loose, up for grabs and Matt Thomas gets a hold of it. Monte Morris lobs it up for Abdel Nader's gnarly alley-oop dunk.

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris drives into the paint and scores a layup while getting fouled. Morris completes the three-point play to give the Cyclones a 10-point lead.
videos.headline: Morris slices in the lane and scores for Cyclones
